					<font face="verdana" size="2">My understanding is the quest to recieve the Purity Belt is in OoT, which sounds right considering the Sisters are all wearing the belts.  Can anyone tell me, do you need to kill the sisters to get the belts, or is there a quest to get them?  If a quest, what is it?<BR>
<BR>
